{"tid":1820911,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"2020-01-10 事件綜合: 粉嶺PTU總部開槍事件 (直至2020-01-12 0500資料所得)","createTime":"2020-01-11T21:56:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-11T06:22:32.000Z","uid":268797,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cdfc1d1fb0179c52f477f9bb250777ca078bb520","tid":1820911,"uid":268797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T21:56:03.000Z","msg":"事件整合: 粉嶺PTU總部開槍事件<br />\n<br />\n日期: 2020年1月10日<br />\n時間: 1940/2000[3]<br />\n地點: 粉嶺PTU總部對開回旋處/ 22&deg;29'23.8&quot;N 114&deg;08'01.5&quot;E<br />\n人: 兩名操廣東話的男人(身份不明,待確), 警車至少一名警員 <br />\n<br />\n事件描述:<br />\n 時間1940 之前,在福安樓嘉福邨事主聽到槍聲,之後錄了大約30秒的片<br />\n時間1940,片中有兩名操廣東話的男人, 一個大叫「救命啊」 , 另一個「你再嘈就拔槍」,之後傳出一下槍聲+火光.(最後一槍?)<br />\n <br />\n-右下角有警車閃緊燈,證明有警察在場(推斷至少一名警員)<br />\n-有目擊者聽到大約16下槍聲,未知有沒傷亡.[2]<br />\n-槍聲後,有人即刻開電筒<br />\n-當時上水火車站B出口有一批防暴(時間不詳, 待確)<br />\n-事隔15秒後, 有一架小巴,一架巴士和一架私家車駛過回旋處<br />\n<br />\n地圖:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jTcmd0s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjTcmd0s.png&h=af9423ff&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n紅X為事發地點,藍圈是片的可能位置, 紅圈是有警察的地方<br />\n證據:<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=l40rLYdvLU8&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dl40rLYdvLU8%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=E2fLMnMY5FLAMirJUdBaWY5RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=4919179b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=l40rLYdvLU8&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n原post: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1819878/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1819878/page/1</a><br />\n            <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1820895/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1820895/page/1</a><br />\n如有其他資料, 請更正, 求 FC 或 廣傳"},{"pid":"7ac4e77ca1fa9465cd923f827a81a97c317665e1","tid":1820911,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T07:25:45.000Z","msg":"【疑點重重！】教大盧曉欣<span style=\"color: red;\">唔係自殺</span>！<br />\n<br />\n<img s